TEST STEPS:

1. Open Verification;
2. Make sure that Entry Editing is disabled;
3. Switch to Ignore Styles mode;
4. Make sure that Entry Editing is disabled;
5. Switch to Ignore Styled Text Mode;
6. Make sure that Entry Editing is enabled.
